=== 行銷 ===
在《星銀島》上映之前和上映的期間，迪士尼透過[[麥當勞|麥當勞]]、[[百事公司|百事可樂]]、[[醉爾斯冰淇淋|醉爾斯冰淇淋]]以及[[家樂氏|家樂氏]]等企業進行了宣傳。麥當勞在其[[開心樂園餐|開心樂園餐]]中附加了這部電影的人物玩偶和拼圖等玩具；百事可樂在其部分產品的包裝上印了這部電影的宣傳圖片；醉爾斯在其運貨卡車上貼了一些從這部電影聯想出的新口味（如「銀河巧克力」和「香草寶藏」等）的宣傳海報；家樂氏則是在其麥片產品的包裝中附加了宣傳這部電影的湯匙<ref name="brandweek">{{Cite news | last = Finnigan | first = David | title = Disney's SEARCH for TREASURE. | newspaper = Brandweek | volume= 43 | issue= 29 | pages = 1 | date = 2002-08-12 | url = | postscript = <!--None--> }}</ref>。[[孩之寶|孩之寶]]也為這部電影發行了一系列的人物玩偶和玩具<ref name="brandweek" /><ref name="bnet">{{cite web | last =  | first =  | authorlink =  | title = Hasbro Arrives at 2002 Toy Fair With Some of the Hottest Brands in Family Entertainment | publisher =  | date = 2002-02-05 | url = http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0EIN/is_2002_Feb_5/ai_82524902/pg_6 | format =  | doi =  | accessdate = 2008-11-24 | archive-date = 2016-01-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160107133247/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0EIN/is_2002_Feb_5/ai_82524902/pg_6 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="toymania">{{cite web | last =  | first =  | authorlink =  | coauthors =  | title = Treasure Planet - Hasbro - Toy Fair 2002 | publisher = Raving Toy Maniac | date =  | url = http://www.toymania.com/toyshows/tf2002/prehasbro-treasure.shtml | format =  | doi =  | accessdate = 2008-11-24 | archive-date = 2009-01-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090108105820/http://www.toymania.com/toyshows/tf2002/prehasbro-treasure.shtml | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

2002年間，軟體公司發行了一些《星銀島》的[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]。{{tsl|en|Disney Interactive|迪士尼互動工作室}}於10月發行了一套適用於[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]、以船艦為主角的[[戰略遊戲|戰略遊戲]]<ref name="procyon">{{cite web | last =  | first =  | title = Treasure Planet: Battle at Procyon | publisher = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | url = http://www.gamespot.com/pc/strategy/treasureplanetbattleap/index.html | accessdate = 2008-11-08 | archive-date = 2012-04-11 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/66pt0zA8o?url=http://www.gamespot.com/treasure-planet-battle-at-procyon/platform/pc/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>；[[索尼電腦娛樂|美國索尼電腦娛樂]]也於11月發行了一套適用於[[個人電腦|PC]]、[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]以及[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]的《星銀島》電子遊戲<ref name="tpships">{{cite web | last = Parker | first = Sam | title = Treasure Planet ships | publisher = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | date = 2002-11-12 | url = http://www.gamespot.com/pc/strategy/treasureplanetbattleap/news.html?sid=2897435&om_act=convert&om_clk=newsfeatures&tag=newsfeatures;title;1 | accessdate = 2008-11-08}}</ref>，同年也發行了一套稱為《迪士尼之星銀島：訓練學院》（''Disney's Treasure Planet: Training Academy''）的電子遊戲合輯，其中包含了三套不同的遊戲：〈海戰炮擊〉（''Broadside Blast''）、〈寶藏獵人〉（''Treasure Racer''）以及〈乙金救援〉（''Etherium Rescue''），而玩家將這三套遊戲的關卡都完成後，就能夠解開隱藏版遊戲〈船形〉（''Ship Shape''）<ref name="training">{{cite web | last = House | first = Michael | title = Disney's Treasure Planet: Treasure Racer | publisher = [[Allgame|Allgame]] | date =  | url = http://www.allgame.com/cg/agg.dll?p=agg&sql=1:42319 | accessdate = 2008-11-08}}</ref>。除此之外，12月時還發行了一套適用於[[Game_Boy_Advance|Game Boy Advance]]的遊戲<ref name="gba">{{cite web | last =  | first =  | title = Treasure Planet | publisher = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | date =  | url = http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/treasureplanet | accessdate = 2008-11-08 | archive-date = 2009-11-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091109112217/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gba/treasureplanet | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 評價 ==
《星銀島》所獲得的評價大多為正面的，不過仍然有一些影評為這部電影寫了負面的評論。其中包括了《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》的影評[[羅傑·伊伯特|羅傑·伊伯特]]，雖然他並沒有直接批評這部電影，但是寫道：「如果能夠再為這部電影上一些傳統的色彩，就能夠使它『更刺激』、『更不花俏』」<ref name="egbert">{{cite web | last =Ebert | first =Roger | authorlink =Roger Ebert | title =Treasure Planet | date =2002-11-27 | publisher =rogerebert.com | url =http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20021127/REVIEWS/211270302/1023 | accessdate =2007-08-18 | archive-date =2007-10-12 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20071012010703/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20021127%2FREVIEWS%2F211270302%2F1023 | dead-url =no }}</ref>。《[[綜藝|每日綜藝]]》的安迪·克萊恩（Andy Klein）對這部電影的劇本表達了批評，形容它「無精打采」，並說道：「但願它的劇本能夠有如它的視覺效果一般有趣」<ref name="klein">{{Cite news | last =Klein| first =Andy | title =Film Review: Treasure Planet | newspaper =[[綜藝|每日綜藝]] | pages =14 | date =2002-11-25 | postscript =<!--None-->}}</ref>。《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的{{link-en|A·O·史考特|A. O. Scott}}形容這部電影「完全不是個對原著的尊敬，反倒是一個製作拙劣、不擇手段的海盜片」，並繼續說道它「根本稱不上是部電影」，且只是「沒有思考、純粹機械的動畫」<ref name="scott">{{Cite news | last=Scott | first=A.O. | author-link=A.O. Scott | title=FILM REVIEW; 'Treasure Island' Flies Into Neurosis. | newspaper=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]  | pages=3 | date=2002-11-27 | url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9B03E1DC1638F934A15752C1A9649C8B63 | postscript=<!--None--> }}</ref>。《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》的{{link-en|歐文·葛雷博曼|Owen Gleiberman}}形容這部電影「僅是將那些動畫效果弄得很新奇，但看起來華而不實、且一點氣勢都沒有」<ref name="gleiberman">{{Cite news | last=Gleiberman | first=Owen | author-link=Owen Gleiberman | title=Booty Pall. | newspaper=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]] | volume= | issue=685 | pages=70
 | date=2002-12-06 | url= | postscript=<!--None--> }}</ref>。不過，仍然有許多影評對這部電影發表了正面的評論。其中包括了《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的{{link-en|史蒂芬·亨特|Stephen Hunter}}（Stephen Hunter），它認為這部電影「呈現了迪士尼電影最純正的一面：它將各個世代的傳統結合了起來，而非在它們之間畫了一條更明顯的界線」<ref>{{Cite news | last =Hunter | first =Stephen | author-link =Stephen Hunter | title =Unburied Pleasure: 'Treasure Planet' Transports to a Swashbuckling Future | newspaper =[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]] | pages =C01 | date =2007-11-27 | url =http://www.washingtonpost.com/ac2/wp-dyn/A43867-2002Nov26 | postscript =<!--None--> | accessdate =2010-09-04 | archive-date =2019-05-29 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190529214127/https://www.washingtonpost.com/ac2/wp-dyn/A43867-2002Nov26/ | dead-url =no }}</ref>。《[[人物_(雜誌)|人物]]》雜誌的莉亞·羅森（Leah Rozen）形容這部電影「具有想像力、豐富的幽默感，且動作輕快有序」，且「那結合了傳統手繪和數位技術的動畫，使人驚心動魄」<ref name="rozen">{{Cite news | last=Rozen | first=Leah | author-link= | title=Treasure Planet (Film) | newspaper=[[人物_(雜誌)|人物]] | volume=58 | issue=24 | pages=39 | date=2002-12-09 | url= | postscript=<!--None--> }}</ref>。《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》的克勞迪亞·普伊格（Claudia Puig）覺得這部電影最值得注意的部份就是它「那巧妙地結合了未來風和復古風的方式」，並認為這部電影雖然沒有《[[星際寶貝|星際寶貝]]》那迷人的魅力，也沒有《[[神隱少女|神隱少女]]》那令人驚艷的藝術效果，但「《星銀島》卻是一個闔家觀眾在假期間一起看電影的好選擇」<ref name="puig">{{Cite news | last=Puig | first=Claudia | title=See 'Treasure Planet' for looks, not charm | newspaper=[[今日美國|今日美國]] | volume= | issue= | pages= | date=2002-11-27  | url= | postscript=<!--None--> }}</ref>。{{link-en|票房預言|Box Office Prophets}}網站上的金姆·荷利斯（Kim Hollis）說道：「這部電影有許多讓我推薦的理由：光是它那壯觀的視覺效果就讓《星銀島》成為了一部非常值得觀賞的電影」，不過她也對這部電影表達了失望，因為她認為電影中的角色「並沒有特別創意性的表現」<ref name="hollis">{{cite web | last =Hollis | first =Kim | title =Drawn That Way: Treasure Planet | date =2003-05-06 | publisher ={{link-en|票房預言|Box Office Prophets}} | url =http://www.boxofficeprophets.com/hollis/animation050603.asp | accessdate =2007-08-18 | archive-date =2007-08-11 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070811075236/http://www.boxofficeprophets.com/hollis/animation050603.asp | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

這部電影曾被提名入圍[[奧斯卡最佳動畫片獎|奧斯卡最佳動畫片獎]]，但落敗於《[[神隱少女|神隱少女]]》<ref name="academy">{{cite web| title =2002 (75th)| publisher =[[美國電影藝術與科學學會|美國電影藝術與科學學會]]| date =| url =http://awardsdatabase.oscars.org/ampas_awards/DisplayMain.jsp?curTime=1228959144749| doi =| accessdate =2008-12-11}}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。它也曾被提名過多項[[安妮獎|安妮獎]]，包括了最佳動畫角色獎、最佳動畫角色設計獎、最佳動畫導演獎、最佳動畫效果獎、最佳動畫製作設計獎以及最佳動畫配音獎等<ref>{{cite web| last =| first =| title =30th Annual Annie Award Nominees and Winners| year =2002| publisher =[[安妮獎|安妮獎]]| url =http://www.annieawards.com/30thannieawardwinners.htm| accessdate =2007-08-10| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20070702195208/http://www.annieawards.com/30thannieawardwinners.htm| archivedate =2007-07-02}}</ref>。目前，它在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]影評網站上基於147篇評論得到了69%的分數<ref>{{cite web | last =  | first =  | title = Treasure Planet (2002) | date =  | publisher = [[爛番茄|爛番茄]] | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/treasure_planet/ | accessdate = 2008-11-08 | archive-date = 2021-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210306161610/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/treasure_planet | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

